text: Émile Arbogast (23 March 1901 - 12 February 1978) was a French swimmer. He competed in two events at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1978 deaths Category:French male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of France Category:Swimmers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wasselonne
